{
  "texts": [
    "Fourteen people-five IT administrators and nine cybersecurity consultants-were interviewed for 55 minutes each.",
    "The data collection approach began with emails to possible interviewees.",
    "Participants were chosen for AI, cybersecurity, and IT management expertise.",
    "The interviewees were asked to volunteer for the study, guaranteeing their agreement.",
    "The research was conducted anonymously by eliminating all identifying information from interviews (Zhao & Wagner, 2023)."
  ]
}